{"tid":1857584,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【緬甸封關】緬甸對來自中國的國際旅客暫停發出落地簽證","createTime":"2020-02-02T08:59:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-02T09:00:28.000Z","uid":79563,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"4bab405dadba4ceb9e7e3746e0ac48b6ac628c51","tid":1857584,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T08:59:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1506202_1_L_20200202165331.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1506202_1_L_20200202165331.jpg&h=e3e41f64&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n緬甸對來自中國的國際旅客暫停發出落地簽證。<br />\n<br />\n緬甸公布，由2月1日起對來自中國的國際遊客，暫停發出落地簽證，中國駐緬甸使領館促請計劃到訪的公民要合理安排行程，避免入境受阻。"},{"pid":"a2c5c575086a5014f82f33b1ad2a1279bab91d62","tid":1857584,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T09:00:28.000Z","msg":"一帶一路呢？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/cis/5e27d5c9fd5cc31c9c2bd9b9.jpg/m0kFCX6kNMq-utWobyizibuiCHvug7sgf2BQin9gUIo?v=w1920r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fcis%2F5e27d5c9fd5cc31c9c2bd9b9.jpg%2Fm0kFCX6kNMq-utWobyizibuiCHvug7sgf2BQin9gUIo%3Fv%3Dw1920r16_9&h=dfe3e043&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}